cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SY, cs.MA, cs.DC 

This paper deals with the problem of distributed learning in a multi-agent network, which involves machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) techniques. The presence of adversarial agents in the network also brings in the aspect of control and system dynamics (cs.SY). The paper proposes a distributed algorithm, which involves communication and coordination among agents, making it relevant to multi-agent systems (cs.MA) and distributed computing (cs.DC).
